To save the pin by other means:
        \n 1. View and save the backup file to other devices through [set BixinKey backup];
        \n 2.Back up to the new BixinKey so that multiple BixinKeys have the same private key.

		 After restoring the factory settings: 

 1. Your private key or mnemonics stored in this hardware wallet will be erased;

 2. The account you created with this wallet in OneKey app still exists, but the assets on it cannot be used because of the lack of private key. Unless you have backed up mnemonics or private keys before, use them to restore your hardware wallet and regain control of your account.
